<h3 id="注意事项-1" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#注意事项-1" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 注意事项</h3>
<p>需要注意的是所有的方法都 必须写在vue的methods中，不允许在外部罗列方法名称</p>
<p>原生的JavaScript的事件方法是不能和vue混用的</p>
<p>同名方法会有覆盖情况，后写方法会覆盖先写的方法</p>
<p>方法中是可以传入参数的,如果方法中没有传入值，默认输入会有该方法的事件参数</p>
<h2 id="v-bind" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#v-bind" aria-hidden="true">#</a> v-bind</h2>
<p>v-bind属性的作用是将普通的w3c属性变为动态属性，让属性具有动态能力</p>
<h3 id="基本使用-7" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#基本使用-7" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 基本使用</h3>
<div class="language-sql line-numbers-mode" data-ext="sql"><pre v-pre class="language-sql"><code><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>body<span class="token operator">></span>
  <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">div</span> id<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"app"</span><span class="token operator">></span>
    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">!</span><span class="token comment">-- 使用动态属性之前 --></span>
    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>img src<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"'./img/'+name+'.png'"</span> border<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"1px"</span><span class="token operator">></span>
    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>br <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>
    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">!</span><span class="token comment">-- 使用动态属性 --></span>
    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>img v<span class="token operator">-</span>bind:src<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"'./img/'+name+'.png'"</span>  border<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"1px"</span><span class="token operator">></span>
    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>br <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>
    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>img :src<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"'./img/'+name+'.png'"</span>  border<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"1px"</span><span class="token operator">></span>
  <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">div</span><span class="token operator">></span>
<span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>body<span class="token operator">></span>
<span class="token operator">&lt;</span>script <span class="token keyword">type</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"text/javascript"</span><span class="token operator">></span>
  new Vue<span class="token punctuation">(</span>{
    el:<span class="token string">'#app'</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>
    <span class="token keyword">data</span>:{
      name:<span class="token string">'java'</span>
    }<span class="token punctuation">,</span>
    methods:{
      
    }
  }<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>script<span class="token operator">></span>

</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><figure><img src="@source/doc/02_初级开发工程师/01_第一阶段/03_前端技术/08_Vue/02_Vue指令/image/image_dpvEzvnokF.png" alt="" tabindex="0" loading="lazy"><figcaption></figcaption></figure>
